FROM AIRCRAFT 
JOIN EQUIPMENT_SEQUENCE ON AIRCRAFT.aircraft_code = EQUIPMENT_SEQUENCE.aircraft_code 
JOIN FLIGHT ON EQUIPMENT_SEQUENCE.aircraft_code_sequence = FLIGHT.aircraft_code_sequence 
JOIN AIRPORT_SERVICE AS DEPARTURE_AIRPORT ON FLIGHT.from_airport = DEPARTURE_AIRPORT.airport_code 
JOIN AIRPORT_SERVICE AS ARRIVAL_AIRPORT ON FLIGHT.to_airport = ARRIVAL_AIRPORT.airport_code 
JOIN CITY AS DEPARTURE_CITY ON DEPARTURE_AIRPORT.city_code = DEPARTURE_CITY.city_code 
JOIN CITY AS ARRIVAL_CITY ON ARRIVAL_AIRPORT.city_code = ARRIVAL_CITY.city_code 
WHERE DEPARTURE_CITY.city_name = 'ATLANTA' 
AND ARRIVAL_CITY.city_name = 'PHILADELPHIA'
